om/?target=https%3A//gitee.com/bajdcc/GameFramework\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;bajdcc/GameFramework - 码云 Gitee.com&lt;/a&gt;)中去了~&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;折腾了一番bochs源码之后，剖出了它的启动代码，其实我无非就是把它的win32_gui模块替换成direct2d_gui罢了，GUI更新的数据结构我就用byte*去传。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;看看后面bochs支不支持自定个io设备什么的，到时候可以自己改操作系统与模拟器传参了~&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;解决完这一套东西，就要继续改进&lt;a href=\&quot;https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//github.com/bajdcc/MiniOS\&quot; class=\&quot; wrap external\&quot; target=\&quot;_blank\&quot; rel=\&quot;nofollow noreferrer\&quot;&gt;bajdcc/MiniOS&lt;/a&gt;了，再要改不好它的bug，那就只能推倒重来了(摊手&lt;/p&gt;&quot;,&quot;commentCount&quot;:1,&quot;linkbox&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;category&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;pic&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;isTitleImageFullScreen&quot;:true,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;article&quot;,&quot;suggestEdit&quot;:{&quot;status&quot;:false,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;reason&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;tip&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;tipjarorsCount&quot;:0,&quot;status&quot;:0,&quot;updated&quot;:1517531454,&quot;reason&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;voting&quot;:0,&quot;created&quot;:1517530300,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/33517169&quot;,&quot;commentPermission&quot;:&quot;all&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;【游戏框架系列】嵌入Bochs&quot;,&quot;annotationAction&quot;:[],&quot;hasPublishingDraft&quot;:false,&quot;paging&quot;:{},&quot;imageUrl&quot;:&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ef278e000706d563aabe9181d18481f6_r.jpg&quot;,&quot;isFavorited&quot;:false,&quot;excerptTitle&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;canComment&quot;:{&quot;status&quot;:true,&quot;reason&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;isNormal&quot;:true}},&quot;columns&quot;:{&quot;learncpp&quot;:{&quot;updated&quot;:1513952410,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;主要研究操作系统、编译原理、图形学，以及其他有趣的东西&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;学习C++&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://www.zhihu.com/